@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20

actor "Manager" as User
participant "AdminDashboard\n(JS class)" as Dashboard
participant "ApiService\n(JS class)" as ApiService
participant "JwtAuthFilter" as JwtFilter
participant "ManagerController" as Controller
participant "BookingListServiceImpl" as BookingService
participant "IBookingRepository" as BookingRepo

== Xem danh sách Booking ==
User -> Dashboard: 1. Click tab "DS Booking"
Dashboard -> Dashboard: 2. switchTab() → loadBookings()
Dashboard -> ApiService: 3. getBookings('all', '')
ApiService -> JwtFilter: 4. GET /api/manager/bookings
JwtFilter -> JwtFilter: 5. validateToken() + extractRole()
JwtFilter -> Controller: 6. Forward request
Controller -> BookingService: 7. getBookings("all", "")
BookingService -> BookingRepo: 8. findBookingsWithFilter(null, null)
BookingRepo --> BookingService: 9. List<Booking>
BookingService --> Controller: 10. List<BookingListResponse>
Controller --> ApiService: 11. 200 OK + JSON
ApiService --> Dashboard: 12. bookings[]
Dashboard -> Dashboard: 13. Render bảng booking
Dashboard --> User: 14. Hiển thị danh sách

== Filter & Search ==
User -> Dashboard: 15. Chọn filter / nhập keyword
Dashboard -> ApiService: 16. getBookings('confirmed', 'nguyen')
ApiService -> Controller: 17. GET /api/manager/bookings
Controller -> BookingService: 18. getBookings("confirmed", "nguyen")
BookingService -> BookingRepo: 19. findBookingsWithFilter(...)
BookingRepo --> BookingService: 20. List đã lọc
BookingService --> Controller: 21. Response
Controller --> ApiService: 22. JSON
ApiService --> Dashboard: 23. bookings[]
Dashboard -> Dashboard: 24. Render lại
Dashboard --> User: 25. Hiển thị kết quả

== Xem chi tiết ==
User -> Dashboard: 26. Click xem chi tiết
Dashboard -> Dashboard: 27. showBookingDetailModal()
Dashboard --> User: 28. Hiển thị modal

@enduml